OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775235955
OL,3,CAppeal to identify four men in
OL,4,Cconnection with Bristol rape
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FImages of four men have been released
OL,8,Fin connection with a recent sexual
OL,9,Fassault in Bristol.
OL,11,FA woman was raped in the Assembly
OL,12,FRooms Lane area at approximately
OL,13,F3.05am on Sunday 29 March.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police is appealing
OL,16,Ffor information that will help to
OL,17,Fidentify four men who were seen in the
OL,18,Fcity centre on the night in question.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
