PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775235955
OL,3,CAppeal to identify four men in
OL,4,Cconnection with Bristol rape
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Almond
OL,8,Fsaid that the first officers arrived
OL,9,Fon the scene within eight minutes of
OL,10,Fthe rape being reported and helped
OL,11,Ftake the victim to a safe place.
OL,13,FShe was able to give an initial
OL,14,Faccount that the suspects were Asian
OL,15,Fand aged in their twenties or thirties.
OL,17,FDCI Almond said: "Her welfare has been
OL,18,Fof paramount importance to us. We will
OL,19,Fensure she has the support she needs,
OL,20,Fnot only now, but in the days and
OL,21,Fweeks ahead.
OL,26,@yD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
