OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775235955
OL,3,CAppeal to identify four men in
OL,4,Cconnection with Bristol rape
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Since Sunday a large number of
OL,8,Finvestigative enquiries have taken
OL,9,Fplace, including fast-track forensics
OL,10,Fanalysis and reviewing security and
OL,11,FCCTV footage.
OL,13,F"Further lines of enquiry are being
OL,14,Ffollowed up, and while those are
OL,15,Fongoing, we hope there will be people
OL,16,Fwho can help us identify these four
OL,17,Fmen.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775235955
OL,3,CAppeal to identify four men in
OL,4,Cconnection with Bristol rape
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"They were not on the scene when
OL,8,Fpolice arrived, but were seen in the
OL,9,Fcity centre on the night in question.
OL,10,FWe believe based off of our CCTV
OL,11,Fenquiries they then headed towards the
OL,12,Feastern part of the city at about 3.30-
OL,13,F4am on Sunday."
OL,15,FHe added: "People will be
OL,16,Funderstandably shocked and upset to
OL,17,Flearn of this awful crime.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@OO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
