OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775235955
OL,3,CAppeal to identify four men in
OL,4,Cconnection with Bristol rape
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Rape offences where the suspect is
OL,8,Funknown to the victim are not common
OL,9,Fand we wish to reassure everyone this
OL,10,Fis being treated with the utmost
OL,11,Fseriousness.
OL,13,F"Extra high-visibility patrols in the
OL,14,Fcity centre have been carried out this
OL,15,Fweek and these will continue across
OL,16,Fthe bank holiday weekend."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@ZO]
